254
00:18:32,780 --> 00:18:34,900
♪What makes your heart♪

255
00:18:35,060 --> 00:18:38,620
♪Stone cold?♪

256
00:18:39,540 --> 00:18:45,540
♪To put on this act♪

257
00:18:46,140 --> 00:18:48,340
♪Saying more♪

258
00:18:48,580 --> 00:18:52,380
♪Making me even harder to believe♪

259
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:55,020
♪Losing you without precaution♪

260
00:18:55,140 --> 00:18:58,540
♪Is more sincere♪

261
