496
00:30:12,500 --> 00:30:13,460
This is very normal.

497
00:30:14,020 --> 00:30:14,980
Don't worry.

498
00:30:18,260 --> 00:30:20,260
I've brought your favorite food today.

499
00:30:20,420 --> 00:30:21,220
Take a bite.

500
00:30:22,460 --> 00:30:23,860
